### CONSORT Guidelines
- Consolidated Standards of Reporting Trials
- Checklist for randomized trials
- Flow diagram template
- Extension for various study types

## Best Practices

### Before Submission
- Verify all author contributions
- Check for plagiarism
- Ensure ethical compliance
- Obtain necessary permissions
- Prepare conflict of interest statements

### During Publication
- Respond promptly to editor queries
- Provide accurate revisions
- Maintain professional communication
- Respect peer review process
- Update author information as needed

### After Publication
- Promote work ethically
- Handle media inquiries appropriately
- Respond to reader comments
- Report errors promptly
- Share data when requested

